project_descr: Enhancing capacity of Palau Government in undertaking consultative and participatory national development planning

donor_name: GOVERNMENT OF TRUST TERRITORY OF PALAU
outputs.output_descr: Enhance the capacity of the Government of Palau to undertake consultative and participatory national development planning. The project is also designed to support planning that takes into account relevant national statistics and indicators which can be incorporated and used to monitor the implementation of plans in successfully moving towards the national development goals and objectives.
